      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      76.58,
      307.36,
      547.47,
      320.64
    ],
    "text": "knowledgeable about the Evidence Ordinance, it is common knowledge that a spouse's evidence",
