      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      76.58,
      327.09,
      547.6,
      341.4
    ],
    "text": "is usually tainted. Even though the Respondents (1-7 and the 9th ] argue that this is a domestic",
