    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      76.58,
      410.92,
      547.49,
      424.2
    ],
    "text": "The wife's evidence was indeed limited. Appellant or his representative did not object to her",
